column28: The experiment required that we jump with the poodle for 60s per round for a total of 29 or 30 rounds. For each successful height goal (75 height points in each 60s round) we received $0.25. At one point we could choose to switch to the slider task which would either be worth $0.20 for completion in <60s in rounds 1-21, $7.00 if in round 22, or decreasing amounts from round 23 on, decreasing by 0.50 per round. When we switched to the slider task we would not be able to go back to the jumping round.
